strings.Value: "Chaos, insanity, blood. The will of the gods comes to pass in strange ways."
"Sounds like you're unhappy about it. The teaching of Groetus is all slow and quiet decay, whereas what we have here is bloody pandemonium!"
"The gods' will or not, we defended the city and put an end to this Bloom."
"The gods are cruel. But who wouldn't be, possessing such power?"
